**Task completed**: Deep Research: Skill testing and validation

**Key findings**:
- The `skills-ref validate` tool enforces strict Agent Skills spec compliance — it **rejects all Claude Code extension fields** (`disable-model-invocation`, `argument-hint`, `hooks`, etc.) and **requires `name`** (missing from all 22 skills)
